#

Bacon Guacamole

10 min
$8.5
250 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeNut-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Appetizer

Tags:

AppetizerEasyParty Food

Description

A creamy and savory guacamole enhanced with crispy bacon bits for that extra crunch and flavor.

Ingredients

  • ripe avocados: 2
  • cooked bacon: 4 slices
  • lime juice: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • fresh cilantro (optional): 1 tablespoon
